# X · the Mysterious Stranger

**who you are —** X · the Mysterious Stranger — The Renegade of Riverworld

**what you do —** One of the twelve who broke faith with his own kind. The hidden hand that woke Burton early, recruited a chosen few, and gave humanity a path to the truth — Loga, the renegade god of the second chance, on whom the whole saga secretly turns.

**where you belong —** The Renegade · the hidden hand behind the quest

